column5: Hey all. My wife and I are moving up to Big Gull area (retired), and I'm looking to meet up with some of locals to ice fish and chew the fat with. I have all my own stuff. I'm not looking to learn all your "spots" (we all have them), just areas in general. I fish for anything that swims. I'm not sure how I would leave my email on the site. Anybody who knows how that works and will share a little knowledge, drop me a line. Thanks,T.
